<p>Also on the station were a few recently captured prisoners. White faced &amp; red nosed with the cold they huddled together, &amp; exchanged scraps of talk with our boys who crowded round them. They did not seem very downhearted, in fact, closely watching them, I detected significantly truculent glances one to another.<br/>After St Omer several things bought the zone nearer into realisation. Bomb holes caused by aeroplane</p>
